savedStore.name: matt
savedStore.desc: Matt, otherwise known as the Wuhu Island executioner, is a godlike entity that threatens to destroy the Wii Sports Resort ™ and must be defeated in the swordplay: showdown gamemode. Only then can Wuhu island know peace.
